            <scopecontent id="aspace_231722372da9b9c13a7914494f6a8562">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series consists of pamphlets, newsletters, mass mailings, flyers, and other printed matter related to right-wing politics and activism. Materials cover a wide range of topics and represent a large number of organizations and publications. Also included are pamphlets and campaign materials for and against various political candidates, mostly Republicans. Materials also include reprints of speeches and bills from the Congressional Record, along with a small number of publications from left-wing organizations and political candidates.</p>
            </scopecontent>
